<p class="ds-markdown-paragraph">Pelajar bisa mendapatkan tiket diskon dengan kartu identitas pelajar mereka. Di beberapa kota, Anda perlu membuat kartu pelajar khusus (contoh: İstanbulkart öğrenci).</p></p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2026-05-29T03:00:00Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-14T16:06:56Z', '$.featured_image', json('{"provider":"external","src":"/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/international-students-in-turkey.webp","alt":"Social life for international students studying at universities in Turkey.","title":"international-students-in-turkey"}')) WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'id' AND "slug" = 'panduan-ungkapan-transportasi-dan-arah-dalam-bahasa-turki' );
