<p class="wp-block-paragraph">What health services are provided in hospitals in Turkey?In order to benefit from health services in Turkey, you must first have health insurance. If you are a member of the SSI, you can benefit from public hospitals free of charge or at low cost. In private hospitals, you can receive services according to your insurance coverage.</p>



