to Study - Turkey University Guide for Students","alternateName":"Road to Study in Turkey","publisher":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"ImageObject","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/hospital-and-healthcare-culture-in-turkiye.webp","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/hospital-and-healthcare-culture-in-turkiye.webp","width":"2336","height":"1760","caption":"Healthcare professionals in a modern Turkish hospital setting","inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"WebPage","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/hospital-health-services-culture-in-turkey/#webpage","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/hospital-health-services-culture-in-turkey/","name":"Hospital and Health Services Culture in Turkey","datePublished":"2026-01-29T11:39:11+03:00","dateModified":"2026-03-15T21:39:19+03:00","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#website"},"primaryImageOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/hospital-and-healthcare-culture-in-turkiye.webp"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Person","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","name":"Murat","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","@id":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9f5b866231ae7aed7a61015846c1f0ab6c5797b065ec200b93c5e9daa87897af?s=96&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g","url":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9f5b866231ae7aed7a61015846c1f0ab6c5797b065ec200b93c5e9daa87897af?s=96&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g","caption":"Murat","inLanguage":"en-US"}},{"@type":"BlogPosting","headline":"Hospital and Health Services Culture in Turkey","keywords":"Health Services","datePublished":"2026-01-29T11:39:11+03:00","dateModified":"2026-03-15T21:39:19+03:00","articleSection":"Cultural Adaptation","author":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","name":"Murat"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"description":"Discover the hospital and health services culture in Turkey. Read our article now to learn